  Luckly for Ragnus the two missles that had hit him before, sent him 
falling as well, thus taking him out of the rockets' path.  About tewnty 
feet above the water's surface Ragnus transformed into his robot mode and 
attempted to slow his descent using his wings.

  Stopping before he was even half way into the water, he drew his laser 
swords and propelled himself upwards once again again to face the other foe, 
despite the gaping hole in his rear armor.
